  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap"><div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Speed Queen Commercial</div><h1>Speed Queen Commercial Laundry Repair</h1><p class="lede">Speed Queen Commercial SQFA7 top-loads, SFNNCA front-loads, SFTX stack washer/dryer, SDGS single-pocket dryers, STTS/STGS commercial stack, TR tumblers, TTI/TTE industrial top-loads, and LTSA coin-op flagship units — our techs service the full Speed Queen Commercial lineup across LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. Alliance Laundry Systems, employee-owned ESOP since 2018, Ripon WI; Speed Queen since 1908 (oldest commercial laundry brand in North America); LA laundromat + hotel OPL + hospital central-laundry specialists; $120 diagnostic waived with repair.</p><div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div><ul class="hero-facts"><li><b>Alliance ESOP since 2018</b> — employee-owned, Ripon WI; NOT Ali / ITW / Middleby / Welbilt</li><li><b>Speed Queen 1908 heritage</b> — oldest continuously-operating commercial laundry brand N.A.</li><li><b>Alliance family single-call</b> — Speed Queen + UniMac + Huebsch + IPSO</li><li><b>LA laundromat + OPL specialist</b> — Launderland, Dadson, Ritz-Carlton DTLA, Cedars-Sinai, Kaiser</li></ul></div></section>

