      <tr><td>Drive belt tension service</td><td>$200–$340</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Water-inlet valve</td><td>$220–$380</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door gasket replacement</td><td>$220–$380</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Coin slide replacement</td><td>$240–$420</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Drain pump replacement</td><td>$260–$440</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Main motor bearings</td><td>$380–$620</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Complete drum-bearing rebuild</td><td>$600–$1,000</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Control board replacement</td><td>$700–$1,200</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Inverter drive replacement</td><td>$850–$1,400</td></tr>
    </tbody></table>
    <p class="small">Most Speed Queen Commercial calls land $280–$650 parts-and-labor. Inverter-drive and bearing-rebuild work runs at the higher end. See our <a href="/price-list/commercial-dryer-repair-cost/">commercial dryer repair cost guide</a> + <a href="/price-list/commercial-washer-repair-cost/">commercial washer repair cost guide</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

